<h3 id="image-content"><em>Image Content</em></h3>
<p>Below guidelines needs to be followed for images:</p>

<ol>
  <li>Image file names should be context based and relates to the image.</li>
  <li>Image should have transparent background.</li>
  <li>Image needs to be compressed/optimized for network calls.</li>
  <li>Image should be less prone to getting outdated in a short time. For example, an image of app and app changes frequently, then we have maintenance overhead.</li>
</ol>

<h3 id="additional-links"><em>Additional Links</em></h3>
<p>The links provided needs to be working all the time. If the link is about to change, then you need to notify <a href="../be-a-contributor/contact.md">us</a> in advance or do the redirection of old link to the new updated link.</p>
